<h1>Thank you very much for reporting a bug or suggesting a feature.</h1>
Type of inquery: 
<select id="br_type">
	<option value="Bugreport">Bug Report</option>
	<option value="Feature Request">Feature Request</option>
</select>
<br>
<br>
Please give us a detailed description. If you are reporting a bug, please give us also detailed information about
your environment (Browser, OS, Versions), how to reproduce the error, what you expected to see and what you saw instead:
<textarea id="br_report" style="width:100%; height:80px;"></textarea>
<br><br>
<input type="button" class="button" id="br_submit" value="submit" /><br><br>
<div id="br_status"></div>
